msgid ""
"Enable SmartGateway. If it is disabled, then all other SmartGateway "
"parameters are ignored. Default is \"no\"."
msgstr ""
"Cumasaigh SmartGateway. Má tá sé díchumasaithe, ansin déantar neamhaird de "
"pharaiméadair SmartGateway eile. Réamhshocrú ná \"níl\"."

msgid "Enable this interface."
msgstr "Cumasaigh an comhéadan seo."

msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "Cumasaithe"

