msgid ""
"Multiply routes with the factor given here. Allowed values are between 0.01 "
"and 1.0. It is only used when LQ-Level is greater than 0. Examples:<br /"
">reduce LQ to 192.168.0.1 by half: 192.168.0.1 0.5<br />reduce LQ to all "
"nodes on this interface by 20%: default 0.8"
msgstr ""
"Méadaigh bealaí leis an bhfachtóir a thugtar anseo. Tá na luachanna "
"ceadaithe idir 0.01 agus 1.0. Ní úsáidtear é ach amháin nuair a bhíonn an LQ-"
"Leibhéal níos mó ná 0. Samplaí:<br />laghdaigh LQ go 192.168.0.1 faoi leath: "
"192.168.0.1 0.5<br />laghdaigh LQ chuig gach nóid ar an gcomhéadan seo faoi "
"20%: réamhshocrú 0.8"

msgid ""
"Multiply routes with the factor given here. Allowed values are between 0.01 "
"and 1.0. It is only used when LQ-Level is greater than 0. Examples:<br /"
">reduce LQ to fd91:662e:3c58::1 by half: fd91:662e:3c58::1 0.5<br />reduce "
"LQ to all nodes on this interface by 20%: default 0.8"
msgstr ""
"Méadaigh bealaí leis an bhfachtóir a thugtar anseo. Tá na luachanna "
"ceadaithe idir 0.01 agus 1.0. Ní úsáidtear é ach amháin nuair a bhíonn an LQ-"
"Leibhéal níos mó ná 0. Samplaí:<br />laghdaigh LQ go fd91:662e:3c58::1 faoi "
"leath: fd91:662e:3c58::1 0.5<br />laghdaigh LQ chuig gach nóid ar an "
"gcomhéadan seo faoi 20%: réamhshocraithe 0.8"

