"Socraíonn sé príomh IP (ip tionscnóra) an ródaire. Ní athróidh an IP seo "
"choíche le linn uptime olsrd. Is é 0.0.0.0 an réamhshocrú, a spreagann úsáid "
"IP an chéad chomhéadain."

msgid ""
"Sets the main IP (originator ip) of the router. This IP will NEVER change "
"during the uptime of olsrd. Default is ::, which triggers usage of the IP of "
"the first interface."
